translations: 强奸罪，强奸案；（尤指对土地的）破坏，糟蹋；油菜；（榨汁后供制醋用的）葡萄渣
强奸，强暴；蹂躏，破坏（地方）；掠夺，抢夺

sentences.sentence: Almost 90 percent of all rapes and violent assaults went unreported.
sentences.translation: 几乎百分之九十的强奸和暴力攻击都没有报警。

sentences.sentence: There're also one or two rapes on campus every semester.
sentences.translation: 每学期也有一两起校园强奸案。

sentences.sentence: Every planet will take on the corporate identity of whoever rapes it first.
sentences.translation: 谁首先掠夺了它，就以那个公司来命名它。
